      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="43705224">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/159908652/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg" alt="金胡萝卜" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43705224/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43705224/" class="">1988年</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/159908652/" class=" " title="金胡萝卜">金胡萝卜</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43705224">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">这片令人欣喜、充满蓬勃希望的田野上，许多事情似乎正被突如其来的经济利益裹挟、扭曲，而刚刚获得财富的人们还来不及意识到迅速发展背后伴生的危机。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-07 22:05</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>这片令人欣喜、充满蓬勃希望的田野上，许多事情似乎正被突如其来的经济利益裹挟、扭曲，而刚刚获得财富的人们还来不及意识到迅速发展背后伴生的危机。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







